high_descs: You will have to turn right and move around to leave the tub.
Walk to the white door and turn right.
Pick the pink bar of soap only, in hand walk away to the right.
Drop the soap into the sink and run some water.
Take the soap bar back and walk it on toward the tub.
Drop the soap into the the itself.
anns.task_desc: To reach, locate than wash an mild dry bar of soap.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the door.
Pick up the bar of soap on the counter.
Go the the sink to your right.
Put the soap in the sink and turn on the water to wet the soap.
Pick up the soap and go to the bath tub.
Put the soap in the bottom of the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Wet the soap and put it in the bath tub.

high_descs: Get out of the bath tub and walk to the counter.
Pick up the soap on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the soap in the sink, turn on the water, then turn it off again. Pick the soap back up.
Walk back to the bath tub.
Put the soap in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the soap, get it wet, put it in the bath tub.
